Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in the southwest quadrant of the GA 400/Haynes Bridge Road interchange, EDISON LAKEVIEW offers the best access, prominence and visibility in North Fulton County. Secondary access from GA 400 is provided via North Point Parkway at Mansell Road or Old Milton Parkway. Haynes Bridge Road provides excellent east/west access and a quick commute for executive and office employees residing in the North Atlanta area. One minute away from restaurants, banking and lodging amenities located in and around North Point Mall.10 minutes from I-285. 22 minutes from downtown Atlanta. 30 minutes from Hartsfield International Airport.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
EDISON LAKEVIEW offers innovative, loft-industrial style office spaces, modern apartments and townhomes, lively and healthy food & beverage options, and eclectic retail on a dynamic, walkable campus that leans into the active lifestyle that today’s modern workforce demands.

Located in Alpharetta, home to more than 600 tech-based companies leveraging the city’s deep talent pool, well renowned power and fiber infrastructure, LAKEVIEW blends technology and nature in a way never thought possible in the “Technology City of the South”. LAKEVIEW is an expansive, cutting-edge mixed-use development with not only direct access to GA-400 from Haynes Bridge Road (Exit 9), but also provides its tenants, guests, and residents a direct connection to the 8.5 mile Alpha Loop multipurpose trail, connecting the site to Avalon, Alpharetta City Center, and more.
